data.text:
This article was last updated on .

Bundles are groups of series. They group different series together by genre, developer, or series. They can be looked up using the $ima command or $disabled.

A list of bundles can also be accessed by using the command $bundlelist on Mudae World.

See also: [[Largest bundles and series]]
